1.0.0.name: wordpress/wp-mathjax
1.0.0.description: WP MathJax is another simple wordpress plugin for MathJax. WP MathJax will add MathJax.js to the header and footer of the page. MathJax.js will be loaded from MathJax CDN. The MathJax configuration can be changed from Plugin's setting page such as different rendering configuration, delayStartupUntil and so on.
